{"word":"Nicodemus","slug":"nicodemus","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Nicodemus</b> - a ruler of the Jews<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=3&verse=1'>Joh 3:1</a><p/>-- A cautious inquirer, but a man of spiritual perception<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=3&verse=2'>Joh 3:2</a><p/>-- Immature<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=3&verse=10'>Joh 3:10</a><p/>-- Fair-minded<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=7&verse=50'>Joh 7:50</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=7&verse=51'>Joh 7:51</a><p/>-- Rendered a loving, though belated, service to Christ<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=19&verse=39'>Joh 19:39</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=19&verse=40'>Joh 19:40</a>"}]}